{"thag16.1:0.1":"Theragatha 16.1 ","thag16.1:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.1:0.4":"Adhimuttattheragatha ","thag16.1:1.1":"“Yannattham va dhanattham va, ","thag16.1:1.2":"ye hanama mayam pure; ","thag16.1:1.3":"Avasesam bhayam hoti, ","thag16.1:1.4":"vedhanti vilapanti ca. ","thag16.1:2.1":"Tassa te natthi bhitattam, ","thag16.1:2.2":"bhiyyo vanno pasidati; ","thag16.1:2.3":"Kasma na paridevesi, ","thag16.1:2.4":"evarupe mahabbhaye”. ","thag16.1:3.1":"“Natthi cetasikam dukkham, ","thag16.1:3.2":"anapekkhassa gamani; ","thag16.1:3.3":"Atikkanta bhaya sabbe, ","thag16.1:3.4":"khinasamyojanassa ve. ","thag16.1:4.1":"Khinaya bhavanettiya, ","thag16.1:4.2":"ditthe dhamme yathatathe; ","thag16.1:4.3":"Na bhayam marane hoti, ","thag16.1:4.4":"bharanikkhepane yatha. ","thag16.1:5.1":"Sucinnam brahmacariyam me, ","thag16.1:5.2":"maggo capi subhavito; ","thag16.1:5.3":"Marane me bhayam natthi, ","thag16.1:5.4":"roganamiva sankhaye. ","thag16.1:6.1":"Sucinnam brahmacariyam me, ","thag16.1:6.2":"maggo capi subhavito; ","thag16.1:6.3":"Nirassada bhava dittha, ","thag16.1:6.4":"visam pitvava chadditam. ","thag16.1:7.1":"Paragu anupadano, ","thag16.1:7.2":"katakicco anasavo; ","thag16.1:7.3":"Tuttho ayukkhaya hoti, ","thag16.1:7.4":"mutto aghatana yatha. ","thag16.1:8.1":"Uttamam dhammatam patto, ","thag16.1:8.2":"sabbaloke anatthiko; ","thag16.1:8.3":"Adittava ghara mutto, ","thag16.1:8.4":"maranasmim na socati. ","thag16.1:9.1":"Yadatthi sangatam kinci, ","thag16.1:9.2":"bhavo va yattha labbhati; ","thag16.1:9.3":"Sabbam anissaram etam, ","thag16.1:9.4":"iti vuttam mahesina. ","thag16.1:10.1":"Yo tam tatha pajanati, ","thag16.1:10.2":"yatha buddhena desitam; ","thag16.1:10.3":"Na ganhati bhavam kinci, ","thag16.1:10.4":"sutattamva ayogulam. ","thag16.1:11.1":"Na me hoti ‘ahosin’ti, ","thag16.1:11.2":"‘bhavissan’ti na hoti me; ","thag16.1:11.3":"Sankhara vigamissanti, ","thag16.1:11.4":"tattha ka paridevana. ","thag16.1:12.1":"Suddham dhammasamuppadam, ","thag16.1:12.2":"Suddham sankharasantatim; ","thag16.1:12.3":"Passantassa yathabhutam, ","thag16.1:12.4":"Na bhayam hoti gamani. ","thag16.1:13.1":"Tinakatthasamam lokam, ","thag16.1:13.2":"yada pannaya passati; ","thag16.1:13.3":"Mamattam so asamvindam, ","thag16.1:13.4":"‘natthi me’ti na socati. ","thag16.1:14.1":"Ukkanthami sarirena, ","thag16.1:14.2":"bhavenamhi anatthiko; ","thag16.1:14.3":"Soyam bhijjissati kayo, ","thag16.1:14.4":"anno ca na bhavissati. ","thag16.1:15.1":"Yam vo kiccam sarirena, ","thag16.1:15.2":"tam karotha yadicchatha; ","thag16.1:15.3":"Na me tappaccaya tattha, ","thag16.1:15.4":"doso pemanca hehiti”. ","thag16.1:16.1":"Tassa tam vacanam sutva, ","thag16.1:16.2":"abbhutam lomahamsanam; ","thag16.1:16.3":"Satthani nikkhipitvana, ","thag16.1:16.4":"manava etadabravum. ","thag16.1:17.1":"“Kim bhadante karitvana, ","thag16.1:17.2":"ko va acariyo tava; ","thag16.1:17.3":"Kassa sasanamagamma, ","thag16.1:17.4":"labbhate tam asokata”. ","thag16.1:18.1":"“Sabbannu sabbadassavi, ","thag16.1:18.2":"jino acariyo mama; ","thag16.1:18.3":"Mahakaruniko sattha, ","thag16.1:18.4":"sabbalokatikicchako. ","thag16.1:19.1":"Tenayam desito dhammo, ","thag16.1:19.2":"khayagami anuttaro; ","thag16.1:19.3":"Tassa sasanamagamma, ","thag16.1:19.4":"labbhate tam asokata”. ","thag16.1:20.1":"Sutvana cora isino subhasitam, ","thag16.1:20.2":"Nikkhippa satthani ca avudhani ca; ","thag16.1:20.3":"Tamha ca kamma viramimsu eke, ","thag16.1:20.4":"Eke ca pabbajjamarocayimsu. ","thag16.1:21.1":"Te pabbajitva sugatassa sasane, ","thag16.1:21.2":"Bhavetva bojjhangabalani pandita; ","thag16.1:21.3":"Udaggacitta sumana katindriya, ","thag16.1:21.4":"Phusimsu nibbanapadam asankhatanti. ","thag16.1:21.5":"… Adhimutto thero …. "}